SIMPLE: pearly
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pearly
<hw>Pearl"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Containing
pearls; abounding with, or yielding, pearls; <as>as, <ex>pearly</ex>
shells</as>.</def> <rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Resembling pearl or pearls; clear; pure;
transparent; iridescent; <as>as, the <ex>pearly</ex> dew or
flood</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>pearly everlasting</ent>⟦br⟧
